---
description: Core product guardrails for Diorama
alwaysApply: true
---

- Diorama is a deterministic spatial canvas, not a full 3D editor.
- Optimize for structured scene editing, inspectability, and export.
- Do not introduce features that widen MVP scope unless explicitly requested.
- Every important user edit should correspond to a command.
- Preserve code-to-canvas-to-code loop.
